link:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juni 28, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104grv1719592389957.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/grv1719592389957.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/grv1719592389957.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jdp1665702627441\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $curword\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"jdp1665702627441___curword_257081\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the word on which the cursor is positioned in the current Unifield.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"jdp1665702627441__topic_d81560e1_d81561e1_d81562e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jdp1665702627441__p_d81563e1_d81564e1_d81565e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curword</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"jdp1665702627441__section_w1012ab1b7b5_w1013ab1b7_w1014ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jdp1665702627441__p_d81566e1_d81567e1_d81568e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">help $text(\"%%$curword%%%_HLP\")</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jdp1665702627441__topic_d53782e1_d53783e1_d53784e1_d53785e1_d53786e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d394878e75\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jdp1665702627441__p_d81572e1_d81573e1_d81574e1\">Word on which the cursor is currently positioned.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jdp1665702627441__topic_d53787e1_d53788e1_d53789e1_d53790e1_d53791e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d394878e84\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jdp1665702627441__d6469e20\">Use in Form components, but only applicable to Unifields.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jdp1665702627441__topic_d53792e1_d53793e1_d53794e1_d53795e1_d53796e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d394878e94\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jdp1665702627441__p_d81584e1_d81585e1_d81586e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curword</span> allows you to refer to a particular word in a field.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"jdp1665702627441__note_w1015ab1b7c11b5_w1016ab1b7c11_w1017ab1b7_w1018ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> This function is valid only in a Unifield; it has no effect in widgets.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jdp1665702627441__section_kfc_fls_wbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d394878e109\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curword</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example uses <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curword</span> to provide\n               context-sensitive help. The user positions the cursor on a particular word in the\n               field and activates the help trigger for that field:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"jdp1665702627441__pre_kwk_fls_wbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger help\n help $text(\"%%$curword%%%_HLP\")\nend; help\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wmy1719769435039.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$curline</a><p>Return the line on which the cursor is positioned in the current Unifield.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7420970\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7420970\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$curword Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juni 28, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $curword Return the word on which the cursor is positioned in the current Unifield. $curword Example: help $text(\"%%$curword%%%_HLP\") Return Values Word on which the cursor is currently positioned. Use Use in Form components, but only applicable to Unifields. Description The $curword allows you to refer to a particular word in a field. Note: This function is valid only in a Unifield; it has no effect in widgets. Example: Using $curword The following example uses $curword to provide context-sensitive help. The user positions the cursor on a particular word in the field and activates the help trigger for that field: trigger help help $text(\"%%$curword%%%_HLP\") end; help Copy Related Links $curline Return the line on which the cursor is positioned in the current Unifield. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}